					LIMS Order Entry</h1>
				
				<div class="col-sm-5" style="border-right: thin solid black;">
					<p style="color: black; font-weight:bold; font-size: 100%;">Facility Name <br/>
						
					</p>

					<p style="color: black;font-weight:bold;font-size: 100%;">Ward/Location <br/>
						
					</p>

